  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Patients undergoing wide surgical excision of their hidradenitis suppurativa areas are asked
      by telephone about their quality of life by standard questionnaires (WHOQOL-BREF, DLQI,
      Skindex, MHF, FLQA-d) and their sexual function (FSFI, IIEF).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
